    ],
    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "Hey mind if I seat here?"
            ],
            [
                "Uh, Sure. Go ahead."
            ],
            [
                "......."
            ],
            [
                "The air is suddenly tight, they look a bit frustrated. And is really avoiding eye contact."
            ],
            [
                "Well, uh.. what's your name?"
            ],
            [
                "My name? Why you care?"
            ],
            [
                "Sorry.. no... name's Victor"
            ],
            [
                "That sounded rude, really sorry, didn't meant to. It's just..."
            ],
            [
                "You seem a bit stressed, are you okay?"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah, no... Well, I'm trying to hide from my boss right now."
            ],
            [
                "She's supper pissed."
            ],
            [
                "Oh, that explains the uniform and the lack of nametag."
            ],
            [
                "Why are you here? Hidin' from your boss too?"
            ],
            [
                "I came here... to the speed dating event."
            ],
            [
                "This is a speed dating event? Oh so that explains the hearts and the corny decoration."
            ],
            [
                "Hey, why is your boss so pissed?"
            ],
            [
                "Let's leave it at me making a little mistake."
            ],
            [
                "Little mistake?"
            ],
            [
                "Well, big mistake. Bad one, might've made her loose a bit of money."
            ],
            [
                "Let's just say that maybe I might have MAYBE left the espresso machine build up too much steam pressure."
            ],
            [
                "So you are saying it exploded?"
            ],
            [
                "It just malfunctioned alright? Oh Crap! IT'S HER!"
            ],
            [
                "Victor hid down under the table. Victor's quick reaction made a little nervious, I instinctively get under the table too."
            ],
            [
                "What are you doing?"
            ],
            [
                "I don't know, you just scared me, and got under the table."
            ],
            [
                "Well it was just for me, not for you. Wait."
            ],
            [
                "What's that smell?"
            ],
            [
                "The table not being too wide forced both of us to be relatively close to each other."
            ],
            [
                "What smell, what are you smelling?"
            ],
            [
                "No... it's...."
            ],
            [
                "is it your hair? Your perfume or shampoo."
            ],
            [
                "I like it."
            ],
            [
                "Suits you pretty good."
            ],
            [
                "Oh... heh... eh..."
            ],
            [
                "For a moment I can't be certain if Victor's compliment is meant to be flirty or if it's genuinely a good perfume."
            ],
            [
                "I mean... Victor said that [he] had no interest in the speed dating. So maybe [he] already has a partner, or isn't interested in me."
            ],
            [
                "And that would make it pretty weird, because looking at [his] face is making me kinda intimidated, and it's pretty weird, because it's making me f-"
            ],
            [
                "Hey are you alright?"
            ],
            [
                "You've been staring at me frozen for like a second or two."
            ],
            [
                "What? No! I'm fine! Yeah, yes, yeah...."
            ],
            [
                "Alright, I think she's gone."
            ],
            [
                "Victor and I return to the seats above the table"
            ],
            [
                "Crazy shift huh?"
            ],
            [
                "And your shifts are like this everyday?"
            ],
            [
                "Well, no... I'ts quite boring most of the time. Not like I would like to be here a single day."
            ],
            [
                "Why don't I leave? I don't know, I've always wanted to be in a band in the northeast."
            ],
            [
                "Why not?"
            ],
            [
                "I don't know... I'ts expensive... And I really wouldn't like to travel that far alone. It's like that frustrated dream we all got."
            ],
            [
                "Why don't you go with your partner?"
            ],
            [
                "Oh no, I don't have any partner. Thinking about that, makes sense for us to meet at this event isn't it?"
            ],
            [
                "Anyways, I need to sneak in into my shift, or I won't make it to the rent."
            ],
            [
                "The bell rings and every other person in the tables get up, same does Victor"
            ],
            [
                "You can pay me a visit later, whenever you want. I'll give you a coffee on the house."
            ],
            [
                "Victor leaves among the crowd of people."
            ],
            [
                "That felt... Kinda oddfun."
            ],
            [
                ""
            ]
